  "S04n384:92": "evaṃpramukhāṇyanekāpsarasaḥśatasahasrāṇi saṃnipatitāni tasmin parṣadi |",
  "S04n384:93": "anekāni ca nāgakanyāśatasahasrāṇi saṃnipatitāni |",
