  "S04n384:227": "evaṃpramukhāṇyanekāni kinnarakanyāśatasahasrāṇi saṃnipatitāni |",
  "S04n384:228": "anekānyupāsakopāsikāśatasahasrāṇi saṃnipatitāni,",
  "S04n384:229": "anekāni ca parivrājakanirgranthaśatasahasrāṇi saṃnipatitāni ||",
  "S04n384:230": "yadā mahāsaṃnipātaścābhūta,",
  "S04n384:231": "tadā avīcau mahānarake raśmayo niścaranti sma |",
  "S04n384:232": "niścaritvā jetavanavihāramāgacchanti sma |",
  "S04n384:233": "sarve te vihārapariśobhitā eva dṛśyante sma |",
  "S04n384:234": "divyamaṇiratnopalitpāḥ stambhāḥ pariśobhitā eva dṛśyante sma |",
  "S04n384:235": "kūṭāgārāḥ suvarṇopacitā dṛśyante sma |",
  "S04n384:236": "layane layane suvarṇarūpyamayāni dvārāṇi dṛśyante sma |",
  "S04n384:237": "layane layane suvarṇarūpyamayāni sopānāni dṛśyante sma |",
  "S04n384:238": "suvarṇarūpyamayāni prāsādāni,",
  "S04n384:239": "rūpyamaye prāsāde suvarṇamayāni stambhāni divyaratnopacitāni |",
  "S04n384:240": "suvarṇamaye prasāde rūpyamayāni stambhāni divyaratnopaśobhitāni |",
  "S04n384:241": "suvarṇamaye prāsāde rūpyamayāni stambhāni divyaratnopaśobhitāni |",
  "S04n384:242": "bahirjetavanasya purata udyāne nānāvidhāni kalpavṛkṣāṇi dṛśyante sma |",
  "S04n384:243": "suvarṇadaṇḍāni rūpyapatrāṇi nānāvidhālaṃkārapralambitāni |",
  "S04n384:244": "vicitrāṇi cīvaravastrapralambitāni |",
  "S04n384:245": "kauśikavastrapralambitāni |",
  "S04n384:246": "muktāhāraśatasahasrapralambitāni |",
  "S04n384:247": "vividhamaulīkuṇḍalasragdāmakeyūranūpuraśatasahasrāṇi pralambitāni |",
  "S04n384:248": "karṇapṛṣṭhottaryāṇi stambhāni maṇiratnakaṭakakeyūrakāṇi pralambitāni saṃdṛśyante |",
  "S04n384:249": "sma |",
  "S04n384:250": "tena tatra ca ramyāvabhāse tādṛśāni kalpavṛkṣaśatasahasrāṇi prādurbhūtāni |",
  "S04n384:251": "tasminneva jetavanavihāre vajramayāṇi sopānāni dṛśyante sma,",
  "S04n384:252": "dvārakoṣṭhe ca muktāpaṭakalāpapralambitāni |",
  "S04n384:253": "anekāni puṣkariṇīśatasahasrāṇi prādurbhūtāni |",
  "S04n384:254": "tatra kānicidaṣṭāṅgopetavāriṇā paripūrṇāni |",
  "S04n384:255": "kānicinnānāvidhapuṣpaparipūrṇāni |",
  "S04n384:256": "tadyathā–utpalapadmakumudapuṇḍarīkamāndāravamahāmāndāravavaḍaudumbarapuṣpaparipūrṇāni |",
  "S04n384:257": "anyāni ca punastatra vividhāni kāṣṭhapuṣpāṇyutpadyante |",
  "S04n384:258": "tadyathā–campakāśokakaravīrapāṭalānirmuktakasumanāgandhavārṣikāṇi |",
  "S04n384:259": "etāni manoramāṇi kāṣṭhapuṣpāṇi prādurbhūtāni |",
  "S04n384:260": "ityevaṃ tasmin jetavanavihāre samantataḥ pariśobhitāni dṛśyante sma ||",
  "S04n384:261": "iti jetavanavihāravarṇanaṃ nāma prathamaprakaraṇam ||"
}